Description: Provides access to functions that simplify the processing of CSV data files generated with FLIR Tools - FLIR Thermal Studio software. Specifically designed to streamline the analysis of thermal images captured with FLIR cameras. Offers a comprehensive set of tools for efficiently handling and visualizing thermal data from FLIR cameras.
